{"tid":236432,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人唔怕死？","createTime":"2017-05-09T17:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T22:16:22.000Z","uid":12679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9f1ed76189e0b7ab7dcfe3f57f21c141ae92b1","tid":236432,"uid":12679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T17:20:35.000Z","msg":"利申:非教唆自殺，請珍惜生命。<br />\n<br />\n死只係一瞬間嘅事。比起生存係香港，有時真係想行出街被車車死算。如果我條命可以換返一個極力求生嘅人，我真係唔介意同佢換。<br />\n<br />\n死，又有咩可怕喎。<br />\n<br />\n由好想要小朋友，到認真考慮不如絕育，一個唔適合我生存嘅地方，無謂害埋小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n這就是香港。"},{"pid":"f0d20eb40ae22e083a589a3cfd016ee4fddb99f6","tid":236432,"uid":82121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T17:22:38.000Z","msg":"唔怕死，但怕痛算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel，我都唔想生個仔出嚟對住個咁無奈嘅社會，我都唔知可以做啲咩，盡自己力量改得幾多得幾多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d7209ebf1bbde388b57e2bbadba1ba1530c99b","tid":236432,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"如果唔痛又唔辛苦既話我都冇乜所謂,死又唔一定係壞事"},{"pid":"057c6a94f69c32aabe66ab77457ff8f9fb790721","tid":236432,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T17:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔痛又唔辛苦既話我都冇乜所謂,死又唔一定係壞事</blockquote>"},{"pid":"751063e87ab49ee6d1b7a4353a2ab793f825449d","tid":236432,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T19:28:03.000Z","msg":"死唔可怕<br />\n係怕個過程"},{"pid":"5af8b81d4ed2157aa637b182baf8bbbbdc3d602a","tid":236432,"uid":17288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T19:34:34.000Z","msg":"唔怕痛 但係怕死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755e62b87cadba9ad7063d71d3268a049792b252","tid":236432,"uid":26053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T19:35:43.000Z","msg":"麻麻地啦"},{"pid":"8d7fae5c5a87dba93243b6fbd41b17631ecc4526","tid":236432,"uid":399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T20:18:52.000Z","msg":"我愛肥仔？你愛我？"},{"pid":"94469c2c2c70828dce07f443dc38c48ec51f1e83","tid":236432,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T20:27:46.000Z","msg":"我對死大概有個概念<br />\n<br />\n只係唔知我死咗之後，我個「意識」會點<br />\n<br />\n呢part 應該係我對死嘅恐懼"},{"pid":"782bfa1ed5ac891a905453aad527a225b96d7da4","tid":236432,"uid":59357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T20:41:46.000Z","msg":"生死有命 有乜撚野好怕"},{"pid":"f77c7001095a0085c6172b4363893dffa55a2b59","tid":236432,"uid":77054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T22:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我對死大概有個概念<br />\n<br />\n只係唔知我死咗之後，我個「意識」會點<br />\n<br />\n呢part 應該係我對死嘅恐懼</blockquote><br />\n你個意識係你個腦到<br />\n死左個腦唔run冇意識<br />\n<br />\n唔通你個意識會send上天堂落地獄72個處女等住你allahu akbar"},{"pid":"9fdc25794a9d69cf5896dd85c87a5cc883fa5cee","tid":236432,"uid":19667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T22:16:22.000Z","msg":"果啲人應該死左"}]}